description._content: Original Collection: Harriet's Collection Item Number: HC366 Image Description: Knute Rockne at Oregon State in 1928 for a school for coaches. Rockne taught four summer coaching schools at Oregon State between 1925 and 1930. Knute Rockne, coach of the Notre Dame Irish, led his teams to three national championships You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more?
